data.description: Immaculate 6 bed/4 bath in Caballo Ranch.  Open kitchen w/ quartz countertops, center island/breakfast bar. Commercial grade appliances w/ 6 burner stovetop. Hardwood floors throughout 1st floor. Upgraded large sliding glass doors. Master with spa retreat bath, guest room with full bath downstairs. 4 beds/2 baths, game room & media room upstairs. Screened back patio. Huge side yard. Views from 2nd story of private greenbelt. Lowest price per square foot in the neighborhood.  Vista Ridge HS. Sellers Purchased the home for 525,000 in 2017.   Sellers have a rendering of a beautiful pool they planned to build before job relocation.
